txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Crooked branches from the twisted creatures of nature in Agamaur. Bring them to Elsa the Bold at the Eglain-camp at Agamaur.
'This is a painful effort, but one that must be done.\n\n'Thank you.'
'We must set about ending the suffering of the stronger creatures within this swamp, too.'
Elsa the Bold, at the Eglain-camp in Agamaur, desires crooked branches from the twisted creatures of nature found in Agamaur.
Deliver the crooked branches to Elsa the Bold at the Eglain Camp at Agamaur
You accepted a task from Elsa the Bold to acquire crooked branches from the creatures of nature within the swamp of Agamaur. You can find Elsa the Bold within the Eglain-camp in Agamaur.
Wanted: Crooked branches from the twisted creatures of nature in Agamaur.
